trans-unit.source: Represents an event that an instance store raises to notify hosts about a condition.
Examples: <xref href="System.Activities.DurableInstancing.HasRunnableWorkflowEvent"></xref> and <xref href="System.Activities.DurableInstancing.HasActivatableWorkflowEvent"></xref>.

Determines whether the current <xref href="System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent"></xref> object and the passed object converted as the <xref href="System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent"></xref> are the same.
The object to be compared with the current object.
Returns <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref> if the objects are same; otherwise, returns <xref uid="langword_csharp_False" name="False" href=""></xref>.

The hash code for the instance.
Returns the XName (namespace combined with name) of the persistence event.
